nodes.text: Dave Boat (born May 9, 1971) is an American voice actor who provided the voice for the Republic Infantry in the Star Wars: Battlefront II video game. He also provided additional voices for Rogue One: A Star Wars Story and Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order.
